{"tid":1957422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全新篤灰系統上線哦！「國泰」員工喜翻天！","createTime":"2020-04-04T02:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T07:56:41.000Z","uid":202464,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"541b847f563d94785a1c6ed51ef5d0653ce4dbeb","tid":1957422,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:25:13.000Z","msg":"張秀賢facebook：<br />\n<br />\n老實講，啲人話要杯葛國泰，我好唔同意，從大陸嘅角度，佢地想國泰死好耐，唔係點解搞完港龍，又要搞港航，只係兩間一間畀人收購，一間吊緊命。<br />\n<br />\n呢舖佢地搵到位入國泰，乘機搞死國泰，咁香港做基地嘅航空公司倒下，最著數咪一眾中國航空公司同港航。<br />\n<br />\n另一問題係，假如控制埋中國領空唔畀國泰飛，咁咪畀其他機場有更大發展空間。喺大家佔緊機場期間，深圳機場、廣州機場股價係咁升，咁咪睇到啲野。所以搞國泰呢件事，中共部署左好耐，國航永遠畀太古禁低，太古傳統上又同中國唔fd，中國咁搞你咪搞你囉。香港人呢個時候連國泰都唔撐，仲話要杯葛，咁香港航空業就冇左一半江山。"},{"pid":"97041bdbef7b9625ca26b6b45a03b28773774ff0","tid":1957422,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"bin C bin C<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8606bcf3dc6822a3eca8267f2d81928793b746","tid":1957422,"uid":310914,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"昵條友收咗因航幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60006f7b121c086812ce6e9a6e714a126174ab4b","tid":1957422,"uid":2189,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"其實Reporting system好多大公司都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9c8930b9f769bc71eabda78698b4e4a965e03a","tid":1957422,"uid":202464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"60006f7b121c086812ce6e9a6e714a126174ab4b","tid":1957422,"uid":2189,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"其實Reporting system好多大公司都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:23:29.000Z","msg":"專門用